              "text": "## Canonical User Intent (already disambiguated by LLM)\r\nConvert the numeric value 3.14 into its string representation and store it in the variable %strVal%\n## functions available starts ##\n{\"Description\":\"Convert object from one to another. html => md, md => html, string => keyvalue list\",\"Methods\":[{\"Description\":\"converts html to pdf, returns byte array of file if no path is defined\",\"MethodName\":\"ConvertHtmlToPdf\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.ConvertModule.Program+ConvertHtmlToPdfInstruction\",\"Name\":\"options\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true}]},{\"MethodName\":\"ConvertMdToHtml\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"content\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"useAdvancedExtension\",\"DefaultValue\":true,\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.List`1[System.String]\",\"Name\":\"markdownPipelineExtensions\",\"IsRequired\":false}],\"ReturnValue\":{\"Type\":\"System.String\"}},{\"Description\":\"unknownTags=(Bypass|Drop|PassThrough|Raise\",\"MethodName\":\"ConvertToMd\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Object\",\"Name\":\"content\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"unknownTags\",\"DefaultValue\":\"Bypass\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"githubFlavored\",\"DefaultValue\":true,\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"removeComments\",\"DefaultValue\":true,\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"smartHrefHandling\",\"DefaultValue\":true,\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"cleanupUnnecessarySpaces\",\"DefaultValue\":true,\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"suppressDivNewlines\",\"DefaultValue\":true,\"IsRequired\":false}],\"ReturnValue\":{\"Type\":\"System.String\"}},{\"MethodName\":\"ConvertToKeyValueList\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Object\",\"Name\":\"variable\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"newLineSeperator\",\"DefaultValue\":\"\\r\\n\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"columnSeperator\",\"DefaultValue\":\"\\t\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"trimColumns\",\"DefaultValue\":true,\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.List`1[System.String]\",\"Name\":\"headers\",\"IsRequired\":false}],\"ReturnValue\":{\"Type\":\"System.Object\"}}],\"SupportingObjects\":[{\"Type\":\"Microsoft.Playwright.Margin\",\"Name\":\"Margin\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Top\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Right\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Bottom\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Left\",\"IsRequired\":false}],\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"Microsoft.Playwright.PagePdfOptions\",\"Name\":\"Options\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Nullable`1[System.Boolean]\",\"Name\":\"DisplayHeaderFooter\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"FooterTemplate\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Format\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"HeaderTemplate\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Height\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Nullable`1[System.Boolean]\",\"Name\":\"Landscape\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"Microsoft.Playwright.Margin\",\"Name\":\"Margin\",\"Description\":\"(see Microsoft.Playwright.Margin type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Nullable`1[System.Boolean]\",\"Name\":\"Outline\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"PageRanges\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Path\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Nullable`1[System.Boolean]\",\"Name\":\"PreferCSSPageSize\",\"IsRequired\"